e\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γαλμι·κὴ\"><span data-text=\"Γαλμι·κὴ\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"Γαμική\">Γ&lt;α&gt;μι·κὴ</span></span></span> | <span data-text=\"ἀχνδρί\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"ἀνήρ\">&lt;ἀ&gt;νδρί</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\">l.4 ἔ | l.5 ε | α | l.6 α | ἀ</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  <div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Θεοῖς</span>  <span data-text=\"καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">καταχθονίοις</span>  <span data-text=\"Πεσκέννις\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Πεσκέννις\">Πεσκέννις</span>  <span data-text=\"Καλάτιχος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Καλάτιχος\">Καλάτιχος</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ἔζησεν</span>  <span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ἔτη</span>  <span data-text=\"ογ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ογ\">ογ</span>  <span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">μῆνας</span>  <span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">γ</span>  <span data-text=\"Πεσκεννία\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"Πεσκεννία\">Πεσκεννία</span>  <span data-text=\"Γαμικὴ\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"Γαμική\">Γαμικὴ</span>  <span data-text=\"ἀνδρί\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"ἀνήρ\">ἀνδρί</span>  </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">Θ</span>❦<span data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">Κ</span>❦<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πεσκέννις\n                    Καλάτιχος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πεσκέννις\"><span data-text=\"Πεσκέννις\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Πεσκέννις\">ΠΕΣΚΕΝΝ<span class=\"tall\" title=\"tall character: ι\">Ι</span>Σ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Καλάτιχος\"><span data-text=\"Καλάτιχος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Καλάτιχος\">ΚΑΛΑΤΙΧΟΣ</span></span></span>❦<span data-text=\"ἔζη\n                    σεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>ΣΕΝ</span>❦<span data-text=\"ἔστη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΣΤΗ</span>❦<span data-text=\"ο❦γ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ογ\">Ο❦Γ</span>❦<span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">Μ</span><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span>❦<br id=\"al5-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Πεσκεσννίαλ ❦\n                    Γαλμι·κὴ\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Πεσκεσννίαλ\"><span data-text=\"Πεσκεσννίαλ\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"Πεσκεννία\">ΠΕΣΚΣΝΝΙΛ</span></span>❦<br id=\"al6-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Γαλμι·κὴ\"><span data-text=\"Γαλμι·κὴ\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"Γαμική\">ΓΛΜΙΚΗ</span></span></span>|<span data-text=\"ἀχνδρί\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"ἀνήρ\">ΧΝΔΡΙ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\">l.4 ἔ | l.5 ε | α | l.6 α | ἀ</p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\"><div class=\"textpart\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><span data-text=\"Θεοῖς\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"θεός\">ΘΕΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"καταχθονίοις\" data-n=\"15\" data-lemma=\"καταχθόνιος\">ΚΑΤΑΧΘΟΝΙΟΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Πεσκέννις\" data-n=\"25\" data-lemma=\"Πεσκέννις\">ΠΕΣΚΕΝΝΙΣ</span><span data-text=\"Καλάτιχος\" data-n=\"30\" data-lemma=\"Καλάτιχος\">ΚΑΛΑΤΙΧΟΣ</span><span data-text=\"ἔζησεν\" data-n=\"40\" data-lemma=\"ζάω\">ΕΖΗΣΕΝ</span><span data-text=\"ἔτη\" data-n=\"50\" data-lemma=\"ἔτος\">ΕΤΗ</span><span data-text=\"ογ\" data-n=\"60\" data-lemma=\"ογ\">ΟΓ</span><span data-text=\"μῆνας\" data-n=\"75\" data-lemma=\"μείς\">ΜΗΝΑΣ</span><span data-text=\"γ\" data-n=\"80\" data-lemma=\"γ\">Γ</span><span data-text=\"Πεσκεννία\" data-n=\"90\" data-lemma=\"Πεσκεννία\">ΠΕΣΚΕΝΝΙΑ</span><span data-text=\"Γαμικὴ\" data-n=\"100\" data-lemma=\"Γαμική\">ΓΑΜΙΚΗ</span><span data-text=\"ἀνδρί\" data-n=\"110\" data-lemma=\"ἀνήρ\">ΑΝΔΡΙ</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001318_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001318_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001318.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001318-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span>  <span>Text based on photographs</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"3\">3: <span>Franz corrected the phonetic spelling in Καλάτυχος, but Korhonen thinks of a stonecutter’s error for Καλλίτυχος (attested also in Sicily: LGPN 3A: 235) </span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"4\">4: <span>Amico, Torremuzza, Franz: ϙ; Ferrara, Kaibel, Korhonen: ο</span>  </span>; </li><li><span class=\"4\">  <span>Amico, Torremuzza, Ferrara, Franz: δ; Kaibel, Korhonen: γ</span>  </span><br></li><li><span class=\"6\">6: <span>ΓΛΜΙΚΗΙΧΝΔΤΙ lapis; Torremuzza: γαμικὴ γιλυκυτάτη; Ferrara; Korhonen: γαμικὴ ἀνδρί; Kaibel: τ(ῷ) ἀνδρί (less probable τἀνδρί) </span>  </span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>To the subterranean deities. Peskennis Kalatichos lived for 73 years and 3 months. Peskennia Gamike [built this] for her man.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo</a></p>  <p>Agli dèi inferi. Peksennis Kalatichos visse per 73 anni e 3 mesi. Peskennia Gamike (costruì questo) per suo marito.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The epitaph contains the traditional formula <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Θ(εοῖς) Κ(αταχθονίοις)</span>, the name of the deceased, the indication of the age (with <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">ζάω</span> in the aorist form) and a second sentence with the name of the dedicant and the relationship of the deceased with the dedicant in dative. The <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">cognomen</span> of the wife is attested in another inscription from Catania dated to the imperial age, CIL 10.7063 = <a href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000347\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000347</a>. Both the deceased and the dedicant seem to belong to the Roman <span class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">gens Pescennia</span>. The text shows multiple diversions from standard orthography, and an extensive and irregular use of hederae.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Amico 1741 257 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002186</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1769 140 n. 37 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002084</a>  </li><li> Castelli 1784 147 n. 41 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002083</a>  </li><li> Ferrara 1829 350 n. 1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002005</a>  </li><li> Franz 1853 5719 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001250</a>  </li><li> Kaibel 1890 <a href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">496</a>  <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072</a>  </li><li> Korhonen 2004 116 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> <p>Irregular letters with serifs: Α with broken bar, lunate Ε and Σ, rhomboid Θ, Κ with long and curved upright, short arms, Μ with five slanting lines at l. 4, Ρ with the bottom of the eye left open, extended/tall iota. Ivy leaves at ll. 1, 3, 4 and 5, vertical bar between Γαμική and ἀνδρί at l. 6.</p> Lines 1-6  10-35  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
